In re Resignation of Jan.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Jan (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1211.]

(No. 91-2229 Submitted November 20, 1991 Decided November 27, 1991.)

The resignation of Joseph John Jan as an attorney, Registration No. 0024519, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
